Any vacancies? I'm between homes.

1029
01:24:35.500 --> 01:24:37.340
You can stay right here.

1030
01:24:38.420 --> 01:24:39.260
I can?

1031
01:24:39.500 --> 01:24:42.100
Yes, there's
a vacant apartment up there.

1032
01:24:44.900 --> 01:24:45.780
I'm kidding.

1033
01:24:46.220 --> 01:24:47.780
You can stay with me.

1034
01:24:48.300 --> 01:24:49.340
Tonight?

1035
01:24:49.620 --> 01:24:53.341
Yes, tonight. And tomorrow night.
And the night after that.

1036
01:24:53.941 --> 01:24:55.061
And after that?

1037
01:24:55.301 --> 01:24:57.101
Don't push your luck.

1038
01:25:04.181 --> 01:25:05.941
I better go.

1039
01:25:07.221 --> 01:25:09.861
Go inside and lock all the doors
and stay there.

1040
01:25:10.141 --> 01:25:12.541
And you're not going to work tomorrow.

1041
01:25:13.021 --> 01:25:15.701
There's better ways of staying
in LA than working there.

1042
01:25:16.381 --> 01:25:18.701
All right. I've just quit.

1043
01:25:43.662 --> 01:25:47.822
I'll just grab a few things...
Hell, I haven't got anything.

1044
01:25:48.182 --> 01:25:49.902
Just bring yourself.

1045
01:25:53.062 --> 01:25:54.582
I better go.

1046
01:26:12.503 --> 01:26:13.703
Go home!

1047
01:26:28.783 --> 01:26:30.103
Go get the girl.

1048
01:26:51.584 --> 01:26:54.864
I would offer you a drink,
but I understand...

1049
01:26:55.184 --> 01:26:56.384
...you're on the wagon.

1050
01:26:56.624 --> 01:26:58.464
That stuff will kill you quick.

1051
01:26:58.944 --> 01:27:01.944
You know so much about me,
who are you?

1052
01:27:06.344 --> 01:27:08.904
I changed the course of your life.

1053
01:27:09.824 --> 01:27:11.464
Four years ago...

1054
01:27:11.744 --> 01:27:13.984
...when you was a narc at Long Beach...

1055
01:27:14.264 --> 01:27:17.584
...you were getting too close,
so we put a contract out on you.

1056
01:27:17.824 --> 01:27:19.664
I handled it myself.

1057
01:27:19.944 --> 01:27:22.665
Drove your car right off the road,
remember?

1058
01:27:23.105 --> 01:27:25.945
But you weren't driving, were you?

1059
01:27:26.265 --> 01:27:28.425
You can't imagine the surprise...

1060
01:27:29.265 --> 01:27:34.105
...when I pulled back a matted mop of
bloody hair to see this woman's face.

1061
01:27:35.985 --> 01:27:37.185
Your wife, right?

1062
01:27:39.745 --> 01:27:41.865
She didn't die straight away.

1063
01:27:43.425 --> 01:27:44.865
It took a bit of time.

1064
01:27:52.185 --> 01:27:54.465
You don't have much luck
with women, do you?

1065
01:30:32.630 --> 01:30:34.510
She's dead. They killed her.

1066
01:30:34.990 --> 01:30:36.110
Where are you?

1067
01:30:36.350 --> 01:30:40.590
They killed her. She's dead.
They killed them both.

1068
01:30:40.790 --> 01:30:44.470
Slow down. Who are you talking about?
Where are you?

1069
01:30:44.710 --> 01:30:46.550
She's dead, Roger.

1070
01:30:48.390 --> 01:30:52.350
Calm down. We'll take care of it.
Where are you?

1071
01:30:52.870 --> 01:30:55.550
I'm not a cop tonight. It's personal.

1072
01:30:56.750 --> 01:30:59.830
You don't know what happened tonight.
There's more.

1073
01:31:00.830 --> 01:31:05.390
I'm going to get those bastards.
I'm going to fuck them. I'm going now.

1074
01:31:06.311 --> 01:31:10.191
We're not going to the stilt house!
We're under orders!

1075
01:31:10.391 --> 01:31:12.671
Then the house will have to come to me.

1076
01:31:12.911 --> 01:31:15.071
They killed them both.

1077
01:31:15.391 --> 01:31:17.951
They got Rika and they got my wife.

1078
01:31:24.111 --> 01:31:25.071
Shit.

1079
01:31:38.711 --> 01:31:39.791
What's the deal?

1080
01:31:40.751 --> 01:31:43.591
You talk to the Feds,
but you don't talk to me.

1081
01:31:43.792 --> 01:31:45.072
That's not fair.

1082
01:31:49.072 --> 01:31:50.592
We trusted you.

1083
01:31:52.672 --> 01:31:54.392
You betrayed us.

1084
01:31:55.952 --> 01:31:56.952
You took our money!

1085
01:32:00.952 --> 01:32:02.072
We want it back now...

1086
01:32:02.312 --> 01:32:04.832
...you slimy little shit.

1087
01:32:06.552 --> 01:32:08.712
Give him more. He likes it.

1088
01:32:42.513 --> 01:32:44.473
Don't try and stop me.

1089
01:32:44.833 --> 01:32:47.473
I've seen that look
in your eyes before.

1090
01:32:48.273 --> 01:32:50.673
They declared war on the police.

1091
01:32:51.753 --> 01:32:53.273
You know about that?

1092
01:32:53.513 --> 01:32:55.833
I heard it on the radio.

1093
01:32:56.513 --> 01:32:58.754
We don't have the authority.

1094
01:32:58.994 --> 01:33:00.154
Cavanaugh...

1095
01:33:00.354 --> 01:33:02.354
...Wyler, Shapiro...

1096
01:33:03.834 --> 01:33:07.794
...Rika, Vicki. How much
fucking authority do you need?

1097
01:33:09.874 --> 01:33:11.274
You got a plan?

1098
01:33:15.714 --> 01:33:18.114
Drive around the front of the house...

1099
01:33:18.514 --> 01:33:20.354
...wait for my signal...

1100
01:33:21.514 --> 01:33:24.034
...and then just go in
and shoot those fuckers.

1101
01:33:24.434 --> 01:33:25.354
They got Leo.

1102
01:33:27.874 --> 01:33:28.954
Be careful.

1103
01:33:36.755 --> 01:33:37.635
Wait.

1104
01:33:37.995 --> 01:33:38.955
What's your signal?

1105
01:33:40.555 --> 01:33:42.475
You'll know when it happens.

1106
01:33:45.355 --> 01:33:47.835
Somehow I think I will know.

1107
01:34:35.436 --> 01:34:36.436
Feel like talking?

1108
01:34:42.436 --> 01:34:43.556
It's the big one!

1109
01:34:48.236 --> 01:34:50.036
Cool it. Watch him.

1110
01:34:50.276 --> 01:34:51.797
Move me away from the windows!

1111
01:36:03.038 --> 01:36:05.359
Riggs, you crazy mother...!

1112
01:36:21.879 --> 01:36:23.559
Holy Christ!

1113
01:36:27.879 --> 01:36:30.239
- You all right?
- Yeah, I'm okay.

1114
01:36:30.479 --> 01:36:31.639
Thanks.

1115
01:36:32.679 --> 01:36:34.839
- Was Adolf in there?
- He got away.

1116
01:36:35.879 --> 01:36:37.879
- I'm going to find him.
- What about Leo?

1117
01:36:38.079 --> 01:36:39.359
What about Leo?

1118
01:36:39.559 --> 01:36:41.399
You're on your own now.

1119
01:36:41.679 --> 01:36:43.000
What do you mean?

1120
01:36:43.240 --> 01:36:46.680
Take my car to the police station
and wait for the Federal Marshal.

1121
01:36:46.920 --> 01:36:48.920
It's been an experience knowing you.

1122
01:36:53.400 --> 01:36:56.600
- I don't want a hug.
- Go on. Lucky if you see him again.

1123
01:36:56.840 --> 01:36:58.520
I had a lot of fun.

1124
01:36:59.200 --> 01:37:00.920
You do your duty now.

1125
01:37:01.200 --> 01:37:03.040
I'm going to really get them now.

1126
01:37:03.360 --> 01:37:05.040
Listen. Wait.

1127
01:37:06.280 --> 01:37:08.280
Is it okay if I sound the siren?

1128
01:37:10.880 --> 01:37:12.320
Loud as you want.

1129
01:37:12.520 --> 01:37:14.760
Really? Okay. Really?

1130
01:37:20.601 --> 01:37:22.121
Check it out.

1131
01:37:22.361 --> 01:37:25.721
Alba Varden is a cargo ship,
not a woman.

1132
01:37:25.961 --> 01:37:29.441
The Port Authority said
that the Alba Varden arrived today...

1133
01:37:29.721 --> 01:37:32.561
...and heads out tomorrow
to South Africa.

1134
01:37:34.801 --> 01:37:36.561
This is the eleventh dock.

1135
01:37:36.801 --> 01:37:39.801
It must be here someplace.
I know I'm right.

1136
01:37:45.001 --> 01:37:45.961
The ship!

1137
01:37:46.241 --> 01:37:47.721
What did I tell you?

1138
01:37:49.321 --> 01:37:52.241
That container there
with three heavy hitters.

1139
01:37:52.481 --> 01:37:53.561
Let's have a look.

1140
01:37:55.321 --> 01:37:57.562
I'll take 2 of them out, you take 1.

1141
01:37:59.362 --> 01:38:03.002
Better yet, you take 2, I take 1.
Pull over to the side.

1142
01:38:50.723 --> 01:38:53.883
- I can't see shit!
- Me, either. What is this shit?

1143
01:38:54.123 --> 01:38:55.523
Got a light?

1144
01:38:57.483 --> 01:38:59.483
It's Rudd's, whatever it is.

1145
01:38:59.723 --> 01:39:01.723
I still can't see shit.

1146
01:39:03.723 --> 01:39:06.883
- You got something?
- I don't know. It's a car.

1147
01:39:12.043 --> 01:39:14.404
Shit! Fort Knox!

1148
01:39:18.004 --> 01:39:19.844
Hell, how much is it?

1149
01:39:21.684 --> 01:39:23.004
Thousands.

1150
01:39:24.684 --> 01:39:26.644
Fucking millions.

1151
01:39:27.004 --> 01:39:29.684
Billions of fucking Donald Trump lotto.

1152
01:39:40.004 --> 01:39:40.884
Look at this.

1153
01:39:41.524 --> 01:39:43.564
These are $1,000 bills!

1154
01:39:45.604 --> 01:39:49.765
With what I'm holding in my hand
I could put all my kids through college.

1155
01:39:51.285 --> 01:39:52.205
Take it.

1156
01:39:59.925 --> 01:40:01.285
Fucking drug money.

1157
01:40:01.525 --> 01:40:03.205
Do something good with it.

1158
01:40:03.445 --> 01:40:05.885
Rudd won't need it where he's going.

1159
01:40:18.565 --> 01:40:20.285
Load the container.

1160
01:40:20.565 --> 01:40:24.205
The next time the sun hits
their bodies, they'll be in Cape Town.

1161
01:40:28.406 --> 01:40:31.086
- Hey, this thing's moving.
- It sure as hell is.

1162
01:40:31.486 --> 01:40:33.966
- What are we gonna do now?
- I don't know.

1163
01:40:34.646 --> 01:40:36.206
Let's shoot our way out.

1164
01:40:36.406 --> 01:40:38.486
No, don't. I got a better idea.

1165
01:41:32.887 --> 01:41:34.207
Our money.

1166
01:41:37.487 --> 01:41:39.447
Make sure they're dead.

1167
01:41:50.488 --> 01:41:54.328
- You go first. I'm too old.
- You go first. I'll cover you.

1168
01:42:09.488 --> 01:42:11.688
- How do we get out of here?
- I'll go this way.

1169
01:42:11.928 --> 01:42:14.248
I'll go this way and check over here.

1170
01:43:38.811 --> 01:43:40.131
Oh, shit!

1171
01:45:49.254 --> 01:45:51.094
Riggs, you okay?

1172
01:46:07.935 --> 01:46:09.095
Drop it, asshole!

1173
01:46:15.215 --> 01:46:17.735
Diplomatic immunity!

1174
01:46:28.055 --> 01:46:30.415
It's just been revoked.

1175
01:47:48.377 --> 01:47:51.057
You're breathing. You're not dead.

1176
01:47:51.817 --> 01:47:53.377
No, don't die.

1177
01:47:54.777 --> 01:47:56.738
You're not dead until I tell you.

1178
01:47:57.578 --> 01:48:01.578
You got that, Riggs?
You're not dead until I tell you.

1179
01:48:01.818 --> 01:48:03.338
You got that?

1180
01:48:03.738 --> 01:48:06.218
You' re not dead until I tell you.

1181
01:48:06.738 --> 01:48:08.738
Now, breathe with me.

1182
01:48:09.018 --> 01:48:10.338
Breathe.

1183
01:48:15.738 --> 01:48:17.738
Rog, in my pocket.

1184
01:48:25.938 --> 01:48:30.578
I want you to throw those things away.
Those things will kill you.

1185
01:48:37.859 --> 01:48:39.619
You son-of-a-bitch.

1186
01:48:41.259 --> 01:48:42.699
I thought you were dying.

1187
01:48:42.939 --> 01:48:46.419
I didn't die on your toilet,
I'm not going to die in your arms.

1188
01:48:46.619 --> 01:48:48.259
You son-of-a-bitch.

1189
01:48:53.139 --> 01:48:56.699
Where are they? Are they all gone?
Did you get the bad guys?

1190
01:48:56.939 --> 01:48:59.219
They been dekaffirnated.

1191
01:49:08.059 --> 01:49:10.580
Don't make me laugh! Jesus!

1192
01:49:13.420 --> 01:49:15.580
Did anyone ever tell you...

1193
01:49:17.660 --> 01:49:20.020
...you really are a beautiful man?

1194
01:49:25.140 --> 01:49:26.660
Give us a kiss.

1195
01:49:28.820 --> 01:49:30.500
Where'd that bullet hit you?

